⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

node.text:
We believe that bonnets have the ability to transform a moment into a beautiful memory ✨ Briar bonnets are thoughtfully and ethically made in the USA at our in-house production studio, with love + positive intentions poured into every step. We hope you feel that love in every bonnet 🤍⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
#briarbaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Briar Baby on August 13, 2021. May be an image of flower and text that says 'CASTINGCALL CASTING CALL'.

node.text:
👋 Portland/Vancouver area! We're looking to cast your adorable babies in two photoshoots 🤗 We're looking for:⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
✨ Babies/toddlers 6 mo. - 3 years (siblings/families encouraged!)⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
✨ Must be sitting up (unassisted)⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
✨ Diversity encouraged!⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Must be available one of these dates:⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
✨ Mon. 8/23 from 9am-10am⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
✨ Wed. 9/1, 9am-3pm (one hour slots starting at 9am)⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
If this sounds like you, please send your child's current age, clothing size, availability and recent photos to⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
casting@briarbaby.com.⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Make sure to share this post + tag your friends who would love to be part of this! Can't wait to see all your sweet babes!⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
#briarbaby
